  {
    "startTime": 98.55,
    "endTime": 100.50999999999999,
    "text": "What do you think makes this a good street food?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.51,
    "endTime": 104.0,
    "text": "It's hard to get like a salad on the go, but just grab a hot dog and get outta there."
  },
  {
